coredns (1.0.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of CoreDNS Debian package
  * Includes systemd service file for automatic startup
  * Includes coredns-zone utility for zone management
  * Includes coredns-validate utility for configuration validation
  * Includes example configurations for common use cases
  * Automatic user creation and permission setup
  * Graceful service upgrade handling

 -- CoreDNS Package Maintainer <maintainer@example.com>  Mon, 28 Oct 2024 00:00:00 +0000
